{{Third-party|date=August 2016}} {{Infobox software | name = Speedtest.net | logo = Speedtest-horizontal-(black).png | logo alt = Speedtest by Ookla | logo caption = | screenshot = | screenshot alt = Screenshot of an internet speed test on speedtest.net. | caption = Screenshot of an internet speed test on speedtest.net. | collapsible = <!-- Any text here will collapse the screenshot. --> | author = [[Ziff Davis]] | developer = Ookla | released = {{Start date and age|2006|04|01|df=yes/no}} | discontinued = <!-- Set to yes if software is discontinued, otherwise omit. --> | ver layout = stacked | latest release version = {{Multiple releases
